  m_text: "Name: DIYA                  Room No:  243\t\t       IP No:  349/17                       
    AGE:2 YEARS\t    Sex:F                                \tMRD No: PICU0023/17 \r\nADDRESS:13,BARACCA
    ROAD,KILPAUK,CHENNAI-10\r\n\r\nWeight: 3 KG\r\nAdmitted On:29.11.2023\r\nPROVISINAL
    DIAGNOSIS: Acute renal failure/Hemolytic uremic syndrome\r\n \r\n\r\nBLOOD GROUP:
    B + VE\r\nDischarged on: \r\n\r\nHISTORY OF PRESENTING ILLNESS:2 year old Diya
    was brought to the hospital with h/o not voiding urine for the past 14 hours,
    h/o passing blood in stools with fever 1 week back. Baby recovered from dystentry
    4 days back . Mother noticed facial puffiness since morning and anuria since
    14 hours .\r\n\r\n\r\nGENERAL EXAMINATION: \r\nO/E : pallor ++\r\nFacial puffiness
    +, pedal edema +\r\nRespiratory distress +\r\nAbdominal distension ++\r\n\r\nCvs
    - s1s2 +, no murmur \r\nRs- B\\L crepts +\r\nP/A- distension + , free fluid++\r\nCns-
    Nfnd\r\n\r\nVitals : \r\nTemp - 98 f\r\nHR- 100/min\r\nSpo2 -91\r\nBp-90/58 \r\n"
